sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Gateway as KrakenD
    participant Nginx
    participant Transfer as transfer-service
    participant Account as account-service
    participant DB
    
    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/v1/transfers + Idempotency-Key
    Gateway->>Nginx: forward
    Nginx->>Transfer: POST /api/v1/transfers
    
    Transfer->>DB: Créer Transfer (PENDING)
    Transfer->>Account: POST /internal/saga/debit
    Account->>DB: Verrouiller comptes, débiter source
    Account-->>Transfer: OK + currency
    
    Transfer->>Account: POST /internal/saga/credit
    Account->>DB: Créditer destination
    Account-->>Transfer: OK
    
    Transfer->>Account: POST /internal/saga/complete-ledger
    Account->>DB: Ledger DEBIT + CREDIT, Audit TRANSFER_COMPLETED
    Account-->>Transfer: OK
    
    Transfer->>DB: Transfer status = COMPLETED
    
    Transfer-->>Client: 200 + Transfer
    
    Note over Transfer,Account: En cas d'échec au credit:
    Transfer->>Account: POST /internal/saga/compensate-debit
    Account->>DB: Restaurer solde source
